Guadian Royal Exchange Assurance PLC, one major British composite insurer, na im talk sey e dey take stake for Nationwide Anglia Building Society estate estate, as part of plan to create different ehn commercial linkage for U.K. and Europe.

Officials no gree talk how much be di transaction, or di exact stake wey GRE go hold for Nationwide Anglia Estate Agents.

But di company yarn sey Nationwide Essex estate agent go sell GRE life insurance, pension money, investment plus more than 1,000 retail mall wey dey U.K.

In addition to di marketing agreement, GRE say Nationwide Anglia don gree to develop life insurance products with di composite insurer.

